00:40:38,860 --> 00:40:43,380
In your book, it's being overwritten again.

750
00:40:43,380 --> 00:40:46,700
It's just like a deeper cut into the page that you see.

751
00:40:46,700 --> 00:40:47,740
It was already there.

752
00:40:47,740 --> 00:40:53,660
And then he slams it shut and begins to dive down

753
00:40:53,660 --> 00:40:55,300
towards this portal.

754
00:40:55,300 --> 00:40:56,740
I give you a reaction before he

755
00:40:56,740 --> 00:40:58,740
does whatever he's going to do.

756
00:40:58,740 --> 00:41:00,579
I mean, I guess I'm just going to hold on

757
00:41:00,579 --> 00:41:04,659
because I'm not jumping off.

758
00:41:04,659 --> 00:41:07,500
I mean, I'm with him in whatever he's doing,

759
00:41:07,500 --> 00:41:10,380
even though he's been a bit of a doofus.

760
00:41:10,380 --> 00:41:15,019
So I'm just going to try and have an arm out to maybe

761
00:41:15,019 --> 00:41:17,139
snag Matamar as we go by.

762
00:41:17,139 --> 00:41:18,739
Oh, that's a great idea.

763
00:41:18,739 --> 00:41:21,619
I see a Goth do that and also do the same

764
00:41:21,619 --> 00:41:24,619
because our poor little buddy is having a hard time.

765
00:41:24,619 --> 00:41:27,539
I summon my crab claw, Mayshant, to also try it.

766
00:41:27,539 --> 00:41:31,420
It detaches from my hand and heads over there.

767
00:41:31,420 --> 00:41:34,699
Bahamut falling in this spiral with these dragons closing

768
00:41:34,699 --> 00:41:39,900
in quickly on you, crab claws zipping out.

769
00:41:39,900 --> 00:41:44,940
And you manage to snag Matamar and pull him in

770
00:41:44,940 --> 00:41:47,619
and hold on to him as you hit this portal.

771
00:41:47,619 --> 00:41:50,820
And everything behind you, you

772
00:41:50,820 --> 00:41:56,779
see all of these demons coming up from what you can presume

773
00:41:56,780 --> 00:41:58,860
is a portal from the abyss.

774
00:41:58,860 --> 00:42:03,220
You see this, you hear this thunderous echoing laughter

775
00:42:03,220 --> 00:42:05,820
coming from closer to the mountain.

776
00:42:05,820 --> 00:42:10,540
And as you hit the portal, Bahamut transforms back

777
00:42:10,540 --> 00:42:16,460
into himself and is suspended in the portal

778
00:42:16,460 --> 00:42:19,380
as you all fall through it.

779
00:42:19,380 --> 00:42:22,980
You see him above as you turn back to look at him.

780
00:42:22,980 --> 00:42:26,100
And he's pulling the, with all of his power,

781
00:42:26,099 --> 00:42:29,059
pulling the portal closed behind you.

782
00:42:29,059 --> 00:42:30,860
Somebody roll me percentile dice, please.

783
00:42:30,860 --> 00:42:32,539
OK, remind me how these work.

784
00:42:32,539 --> 00:42:34,380
I have a zero, zero, and an eight.

785
00:42:34,380 --> 00:42:36,900
Is that 80 or is that eight?

786
00:42:36,900 --> 00:42:39,579
That's eight.

787
00:42:39,579 --> 00:42:41,420
Which could be great or terrible.

788
00:42:41,420 --> 00:42:43,019
You never know with a percentile dice.

789
00:42:43,019 --> 00:42:43,900
All of the numbers.

790
00:42:43,900 --> 00:42:47,299
All of the numbers could be great or terrible.

791
00:42:47,299 --> 00:42:53,659
Colors and light zip past you until all of these images

792
00:42:54,460 --> 00:42:58,859
of Toriel and of all these fantastical, mystical places

793
00:42:58,859 --> 00:43:02,500
and of this dark, terrible place.

794
00:43:02,500 --> 00:43:04,539
And then you land hard.

795
00:43:04,539 --> 00:43:05,899
All of you.

796
00:43:05,899 --> 00:43:07,420
The wind is knocked out of you

797
00:43:07,420 --> 00:43:10,699
and there's this radiating heat around you.

798
00:43:10,699 --> 00:43:16,420
You're in this dim, red lit cave, it feels like.

799
00:43:16,420 --> 00:43:17,699
You get up and you look around

800
00:43:17,699 --> 00:43:19,940
and you see all of your travel companions.

801
00:43:19,940 --> 00:43:22,659
And Goth, you're huddled close.

802
00:43:22,659 --> 00:43:24,059
You have Mademar huddled close,

803
00:43:24,059 --> 00:43:27,339
Rax is off into the side and standing up

804
00:43:27,339 --> 00:43:30,739
and pawing at the dirt.

805
00:43:30,739 --> 00:43:35,259
Do we see, sorry, did the portal close above us?

806
00:43:35,259 --> 00:43:39,379
So we saw him close it above it.

807
00:43:39,379 --> 00:43:41,460
I will be pumping a quick Spare the Dying

808
00:43:41,460 --> 00:43:43,059
into Mademar, just in case.

809
00:43:43,059 --> 00:43:45,379
Sure, yeah.

810
00:43:45,379 --> 00:43:46,739
What does Spare the Dying look like

811
00:43:46,739 --> 00:43:48,940
and remind me what it does?

812
00:43:48,940 --> 00:43:51,179
You touch a living creature that has zero hit points.

813
00:43:51,179 --> 00:43:52,339
The creature becomes stable.

814
00:43:52,340 --> 00:43:55,340
The spell has no effect on undead or constructs.

815
00:43:55,340 --> 00:43:55,820
OK, yeah.

816
00:43:55,820 --> 00:43:57,180
So I'm assuming since he was.

817
00:43:57,180 --> 00:44:00,500
You can stabilize him, yeah.

818
00:44:00,500 --> 00:44:03,140
Yeah, he kind of coughs back to life.

819
00:44:03,140 --> 00:44:05,579
Does anybody know where we are?

820
00:44:05,579 --> 00:44:08,420
It's hot.

821
00:44:08,420 --> 00:44:13,860
I mean, it is so hot in here.

822
00:44:13,860 --> 00:44:19,940
But I mean, Bahamut must have had a plan that we would.

823
00:44:19,940 --> 00:44:22,659
What, meet up later?

824
00:44:22,659 --> 00:44:25,019
I don't know.

825
00:44:25,019 --> 00:44:26,139
Well, we can't stay here.

826
00:44:26,139 --> 00:44:29,579
We got to figure out where we are, right?

827
00:44:29,579 --> 00:44:31,780
Flammikins gets up and starts to stumble off

828
00:44:31,780 --> 00:44:34,539
towards a cave opening.

829
00:44:34,539 --> 00:44:35,059
Well, hold on.

830
00:44:35,059 --> 00:44:37,260
I think we should probably stay together.

831
00:44:37,260 --> 00:44:39,260
Well, I thought you were going to follow me.

832
00:44:39,260 --> 00:44:41,700
Wow, it's fucking like leadership.

833
00:44:41,700 --> 00:44:43,019
Or are you giving off here?

834
00:44:43,019 --> 00:44:45,700
OK, I'll follow you into a dark cave.

835
00:44:45,700 --> 00:44:48,940
You all carry forward down this corridor

836
00:44:48,940 --> 00:44:51,820
and you hear this rumble.

837
00:44:51,820 --> 00:44:55,500
It's like low growl coming from up ahead.

838
00:44:55,500 --> 00:44:59,099
That's like resonating the walls.

839
00:44:59,099 --> 00:45:02,619
And you round a corner into this wide chamber.

840
00:45:02,619 --> 00:45:08,300
There's this huge throne across the other side.

841
00:45:08,300 --> 00:45:10,460
And in this chamber, there are

842
00:45:10,460 --> 00:45:14,220
six chromatic dragons around the outside.

843
00:45:14,220 --> 00:45:17,539
And in the throne is Tiamat.

